strings: <voice_0x01001516><se_low>High Priest Rolo: ...So that's the plan.
<voice_0x01001517><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Right, let's get to work!
<voice_0x01001518><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Goddess on high! Please, let this succeed!
<voice_0x01001519><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Uuurgh! Ouch! Oh, it hurts! Aahh! Aahh!

<voice_0x0100151A><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Somebody! Help me!
My stomach... The pain's unbearable!

<voice_0x0100151B><se_low>Yangus: Here, are you awright, mate!?
Wot's wrong wiv ya?
<voice_0x0100151C><se_high>Jessica: He's going to die! Ah, heeeelp!

<voice_0x0100151D><se_low>High Priest Rolo: M-My gold rosary! I swallowed it!
And now the pain is unbearable!

<voice_0x0100151E><se_low>Yangus: Wot!? Ya swallowed yer gold rosary!?
Wot on earth did you go an' do that for, eh!?
<voice_0x0100151F><se_low>High Priest Rolo: It's so valuable! I did not want to lose it!
<voice_0x01001520><se_low>High Priest Rolo: When they brought us here, I swallowed it so no one would take it from me!

<voice_0x01001521><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Ouch! It's so painful!
My GOLD rosary is digging into me!
Ouch!

<voice_0x01001522><se_low>*: Strewth! D'you hear that, mate?
He said it's made of gold!
<voice_0x01001523><se_low>*: Hey, old man! Feelin' a bit crook, are ya?
<voice_0x01001524><se_low>*: We'll look after you! At least 'til that gold rosary comes out of you. One way or another!
<voice_0x01001525><se_low>*: He he he! We'd better give him a good check over, just in case there's anything else in there!

<voice_0x01001526><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Thank you! You are so kind!
Thank you so much!
<voice_0x01001527><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Could you just do one thing first...?
<voice_0x01001528><se_low>*: Oh, yeah!? What's that?
<voice_0x01001529><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Take a little nap, you halfwit nurses!
<voice_0x0100152A><se_low>*: Hooly dooly!
<voice_0x0100152B><se_low>*: Aaaaaargh!
<voice_0x0100152C><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Right then! Now!
<voice_0x0100152D><se_low>*: Th-They're gettin' away!
<voice_0x0100152E><se_low>Yangus: Why ain't it movin'!? Is it bust or somefin'?
<voice_0x0100152F><se_high>Jessica: Ah! It's that lever! Whenever the guards change over, one of them has to operate it.

<voice_0x01001530><se_high>Jessica: Someone will have to stay behind.
Otherwise we're all stuck here!
<voice_0x01001531><se_low>Yangus: I'll do it! It's me duty to the guv!
<voice_0x01001533><se_low>Yangus: You!? Wot are you gonna do if ya don't get out wiv everyone else, eh?
<voice_0x01001534><se_low>Yangus: Them nurses'll finish ya off when they come round! You ain't no match for them!
<voice_0x01001535><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Even if I were to escape from here, the church would catch up with me soon enough.
<voice_0x01001536><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Let me do this. Please...
<voice_0x01001537><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Just promise that you'll find out what really caused His Holiness's death.
<voice_0x01001538><se_low>High Priest Rolo: It's imperative that the truth is made public!
<voice_0x01001539><se_low>Yangus: Yer a good bloke, Rolo!
<voice_0x0100153A><se_low>High Priest Rolo: You must find out the truth!

<voice_0x0100153B><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Don't worry about me!
Just make sure you escape!

<voice_0x0100153C><se_low>High Priest Rolo: You must learn the truth behind
His Holiness's death!
<voice_0x0100153D><se_low>High Priest Rolo: So, you two oafs are awake? I'm sorry to have to inform you that I will not be producing a gold rosary from either end in the foreseeable future.
<voice_0x0100153E><se_low>High Priest Rolo: I'm ready. Do what you will with me!
<voice_0x0100153F><se_low>King Trode: Ah-haaah!

<voice_0x01001540><se_low>King Trode: You inconsiderate nincompoops!
Where on earth have you been!?
I've been beside myself with worry!

<voice_0x01001544><se_low>King Trode: Well anyway, never mind!
At least you're all safe.

<voice_0x01001545><se_low>King Trode: I suppose you've heard?
The Lord High Priest has been killed.
And it's quite clear who the culprit is!

<voice_0x01001546><se_low>King Trode: No time to shilly-shally!
Come along, <hero>!
We must go!
<voice_0x01001532><se_low>High Priest Rolo: No, wait! I'll do it.
<voice_0x01001541><se_high>Red: You wouldn't believe wot an 'ard time I've 'ad trackin' you lot down.
<voice_0x01001542><se_high>Red: Never thought I'd find ya banged up on Purgatory bleedin' Island. It don't get much worse than this, eh?
